# ViaLaNet Polygon Widget

Standalone PyQt widget for polygon extraction, editing, and export.

## Run

```powershell
pip install -e .
polygon-widget
```

## Local Entrypoint

```powershell
python main.py
```

## Alternative

```powershell
python -m polygon_widget
```
